title: Dell PowerVault ME5: Sensors
agents: dell_powervault_me5
catalog: hw/storagehw/dell
license: GPLv2
distribution: Sher Zaman
description:
 Monitors the non-temperature enclosure sensors of a Dell PowerVault ME5 system,
 grouped by sensor type (voltage, current and the capacitor/supercap pack). One
 service is created per sensor type and aggregates every sensor of that type:
 the service reports the worst state across its members and names any sensor
 that is not OK, with all readings shown in the service details.

 The mapping of the not-OK condition is configurable via the "Dell PowerVault
 ME5 sensor" ruleset.

item:
 The sensor type (for example {"Voltage"} or {"Current"}).

discovery:
 One service is created per non-temperature sensor type present.
